summary: Use this API to get SKU list
description: Use this API to get SKU list

query.name: operate_Time_From
query.description: Inventory operate time from. This param is Required

query.name: operate_Time_To
query.description: Inventory operate time to. This param is Required.We suggest that operate_time_to - operate_time_from < 6 months

common.name: app_key
common.description: Unique app ID issued by LAZADA Open Platform console when you apply for an app category

common.name: timestamp
common.description: The time stamp of the request e.g. 1517820392000 (which translates to 5 February 2018 08:46:32) with less than 7200s difference from UTC time

common.name: sign_method
common.description: The HMAC hash algorithm you are using to calculate your signature

request_examples.code:
client = LazopApiClient::Client.new(url, appkey, appSecret)
request = LazopApiClient::Request.new('/fbl/inventory_changed_sku/get','GET')
request.add_api_parameter("warehouse_code", "OMS-LAZADA-MY-W-1")
request.add_api_parameter("page", "1")
request.add_api_parameter("per_page", "20")
request.add_api_parameter("market_place", "LAZADA_SG")
request.add_api_parameter("operate_Time_From", "2019-07-23")
request.add_api_parameter("operate_Time_To", "2019-08-24")
response = client.execute(request, accessToken)
puts response.success?
puts response.body
